\begin_layout Standard
本文试图通过一些例子完成本学期大学物理知识体系的构建.
 正如Warrior和众多大学教师一直建议的那样, 学习整理的过程永远要比结果更重要, 更值得享受.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
Yeats有一句名言：“教育不是注满一桶水, 而是点燃一把火.
 ”他说得既对也错.
 你必 须“给桶注一点水”, 这本书当然可以帮助你完成这部分的教育.
 毕竟, 当你去 Google 面试 时, 他们会问你一个关于如何使用信号量的技巧问题, 确切地知道信号量是什么感觉真好,  对吧?
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
但是, Yeats的更主要的观点显然是正确的：教育的真正要义是让你对某些事情感兴趣, 这不仅仅是搞明白课上学习的东西, 得个好成绩.
 更重要的是课后可以独立了解这个主题的更多东西.
 正如我们的父亲（作者的父亲 Vedat Arpaci）曾说过的, “在课堂以外学习.
 ”
\end_layout

\begin_layout Quote
我们编写本书的目的是激发你对操作系统的兴趣.
 这就可以让你能自行了解有关操作系统的更多知识, 进而 可以与你的教授讨论, 甚至参与该领域相关的那些令人兴奋的研究.
 这是一个伟大的 领域: 这里有充满了激动人心和精妙的想法, 它们以深刻而重要的方式塑造了计算历史.
 虽然我们知道这 团火不会为你们所有人点燃, 但我们希望这能对许多人, 甚至是少数人有所帮助.
 因为一旦这团火 被点燃, 那你就真正有能力做出伟大的事情.
 因此, 教育过程的真正意义在于：一往无前, 学习更 多的新的和引人入胜, 美妙绝伦的知识, 通过学习不断成熟, 最重要的是, 找到能为你点燃那团火的人.
  – 《Operating Systems: Three Easy Pieces》
\end_layout

\begin_layout Part
核心内容回顾
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
运动学
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
一.
 运动与坐标系的选取.
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 矢量与微积分的观点
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
2.
 描述运动的三个物理量
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(1) 微分关系
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\mathbf{r} & =x_{i}\mathbf{i}+y_{j}\mathbf{j}+z_{k}\mathbf{k}\\
\mathbf{v} & =v_{i}\mathbf{i}+v_{j}\mathbf{j}+v_{k}\mathbf{k}\\
\mathbf{a} & =a_{i}\mathbf{i}+a_{j}\mathbf{j}+a_{k}\mathbf{k}
\end{align*}

\end_inset

以及有微分关系
\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{v}=\frac{\dd\bs r}{\dd\bs t},\bs a=\frac{\dd\bs v}{\dd\bs t}$
\end_inset

, 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(a)推论: 求
\begin_inset Formula $\bs{v,t}$
\end_inset

对于
\begin_inset Formula $\bs x$
\end_inset

的关系: 使用关系
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\dd\bs r}{\dd\bs x}\frac{\dd\bs x}{\dd\bs t}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(2) 积分关系
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\dd\bs r & =\bs v\dd t,\vec r=\vec{r_{0}}+\int_{0}^{t}\vec v\dd t\\
\dd\bs v & =\bs a\dd t,\vec v=\vec{a_{0}}+\int_{0}^{t}\vec a\dd t
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 坐标系的选取: 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(1) 直角坐标
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(2) 自然坐标
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(3) 极坐标
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
4.
 圆周运动
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(1) 描述圆周运动的物理量: 角速度
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

, 角加速度
\begin_inset Formula $\beta$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(a) 之间关系: 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega=\frac{\dd\theta}{\dd t},\beta=\frac{\dd\omega}{\dd t};\theta=\theta_{0}+\int_{0}^{t}\omega\dd t,\omega=\omega_{0}+\int_{0}^{t}\beta\dd t.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(2) 自然坐标系中的加速度: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec a=\vec{a_{n}}+\vec{a_{t}}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(a) 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{n}:$
\end_inset

法向分量, 指向圆心
\begin_inset Formula $a_{n}=\frac{v^{2}}{R}=\omega^{2}R$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(b) 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{t}:$
\end_inset

切向分量, 沿轨迹方向 
\begin_inset Formula $a_{t}=\frac{\dd v}{\dd t}=R\frac{\dd\omega}{\dd t}=R\beta.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
二.
 Newton运动定律及其延伸
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 Newton第二定律: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec F=\frac{\dd(m\vec v)}{\dd t},\vec F=m\vec a;$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
2.
 动量与冲量
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
定义.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec F\dd t=\dd(m\vec v),\dd\vec I=\dd\vec P,\vec I=\Delta\vec P$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
质点动量定理.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}\vec F\dd t=m\vec{v_{2}}-m\vec{v_{1}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
质点系动量定理.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{t_{1}}^{t_{2}}\left(\sum_{i}\vec{F_{i_{\text{外}}}}\right)\dd t=\sum_{i}m_{i}\vec{v_{i}}_{2}-\sum_{i}m_{i}\vec{v_{i}}_{1}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
动量守恒定律.
 当
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{i}\vec{F_{i_{\text{外}}}}=0,\sum_{i}m_{i}v_{i}$
\end_inset

守恒.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 
\uwave on
\color teal
角动量
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
定义.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec L=\vec r\times m\vec v$
\end_inset

.
 其中
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

是从原点当前点的位置矢量.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
角动量守恒定律: 有心力(受力指向圆心, 外力矩为0)
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
4.
 功: 
\begin_inset Formula $A=\int_{\vec{r_{1}}}^{\vec{r_{2}}}\vec F\cdot\dd\vec r$
\end_inset

, 可以分坐标求和.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
5.
 保守力场中
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

点的势能: 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{p}(P)=\int_{(P)}^{(\text{零势能点)}}\vec{F_{\text{保守}}}\cdot\dd\vec r$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
6.
 质点的动能定理: 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\text{外}}+A_{\text{内}}=\Delta\left(\sum_{i}E_{k_{i}}\right)=\sum_{i}\frac{1}{2}m_{i}v_{i_{2}}^{2}-\sum_{i}\frac{1}{2}m_{i}v_{i_{1}}^{2}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
7.
 功能原理: 
\begin_inset Formula $A_{\text{外}}+A_{\text{非保守内}}=\Delta\left(\sum_{i}E_{i}\right),E=E_{k}+E_{P}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
机械能守恒定律: 当只有保守力做功的时候, 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{i}E_{i}$
\end_inset

守恒.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
三.
 刚体的定轴转动
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 运动的描述
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
描述: 圆周运动
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
刚体定轴转动定律: 
\begin_inset Formula $M=J\beta,J=\sum_{i}m_{i}r_{i}^{2}=\int_{M}r^{2}\dd m$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
2.
 
\uwave on
\color teal
刚体定轴转动的动能定理
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
描述: 
\begin_inset Formula $A=\Delta E_{k},A=\int_{\theta_{1}}^{\theta_{2}}M\dd\theta,E_{k}=\frac{1}{2}J\omega^{2}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
机械能守恒定律: 当只有保守力做功, 
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{i}E_{i}$
\end_inset

守恒.
 写作
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
E=E_{k}+E_{p}=\left(\frac{1}{2}mv^{2}+\red{\frac{1}{2}J\omega^{2}}\right)+\left(mgh+\red{mgh_{\text{重心}}}\right)
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 
\uwave on
\color teal
角动量
\uwave default
\color inherit
: 
\begin_inset Formula $L=J\omega$
\end_inset

, 方向垂直于转动平面.
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
角动量守恒.
 当合外力矩为0, 
\begin_inset Formula $L=J\omega$
\end_inset

守恒
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
四.
 相对论
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 基本理论
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(a) 相对性原理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(b) 光速不变性
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
2.
 时间/地点相同的变换
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
变换因子 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\gamma=\frac{1}{\sqrt{1-\frac{u^{2}}{c^{2}}}}\geq1
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 
\uwave on
\color teal
Lorentz变换
\uwave default
\color inherit
: 相对于
\begin_inset Formula $x-x'$
\end_inset

方向的时空间隔变换:
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\Delta x=\gamma(\Delta x'+u\Delta t') & ,\Delta x'=\gamma(\Delta x-u\Delta t)\\
\Delta t=\gamma\left(\Delta t'+\frac{u\Delta x'}{c^{2}}\right) & ,\Delta t'=\gamma\left(\Delta t'-\frac{u\Delta x'}{c^{2}}\right)
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
4.
 
\uwave on
\color teal
相对论的动力学关系
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(a) 运动的质量.
 
\begin_inset Formula $m=\gamma m_{0}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(b) 相对论动量.
 
\begin_inset Formula $p=\gamma m_{0}u$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(c) 相对论动能.
 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{k}=E-E_{0}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(d) 动能, 静止能量: 
\begin_inset Formula $E=\gamma m_{0}c^{2},E_{0}=m_{0}c^{2}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
电磁学
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
一.
 真空中的静电场
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 点电荷模型
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
a.
 库伦定律: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec f=\frac{1}{4\pi\epsilon_{0}}\frac{q_{1}q_{2}}{r^{2}}\vec{e_{r}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
b.
 点电荷形成的电场: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec E=\ef\frac{q}{r^{2}}\vec{e_{r}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
2.
 电场叠加原理: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec E=\sum_{i}\vec{E_{i}}=\sum_{i}\ef\frac{q_{i}}{r_{i}^{2}}\vec{e_{r_{i}}}=\int_{Q}\dd\vec E=\int_{Q}\ef\frac{\dd q}{r^{2}}\vec{e_{r}}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
a.
 模型电场
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
长直导线.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec E=\frac{1}{2\pi\eqs_{0}}\frac{\lambda}{r}\vec{e_{i}}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
大平面.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec E=\frac{\sigma}{2\eqs_{0}}\vec{e_{n}}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
b.
 Gauss定理
\begin_inset Formula $\oint_{S}\vec E\cdot\dd\vec S=\frac{1}{\eqs_{0}}\sum_{i}q_{i\text{内}},\phi_{c}=\int_{S}\vec E\cdot\dd\vec S.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
应用: 
\uwave on
\color teal
用Gauss定理求对称性电场分布: 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
球体: 
\begin_inset Formula $E4\pi r^{2}=q_{in}/\eqs_{0}\implies E=\frac{q_{in}}{\eqs_{0}4\pi r^{2}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
圆柱体: 
\begin_inset Formula $E2\pi rh=q_{in}/\eqs_{0}\implies E=\frac{q_{in}}{\eqs_{0}2\pi rh}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
平面: 
\begin_inset Formula $E2S_{\text{底}}=q_{in}/\eqs_{0}\implies E=\frac{q_{in}}{\eqs_{0}2S_{\text{底}}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 电势能与电场力做的功
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
a.
 电场力做的功
\begin_inset Formula $W_{a}-W_{b}=q_{0}(V_{a}-V_{b})=q_{0}\int_{(a)}^{(b)}\vec E\cdot\dd\vec r$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
b.
 电势 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{P}(P)=\int_{(P)}^{(\text{零势点)}}\vec E\cdot\dd\vec r$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
c.
 点电荷的电势 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{\text{点电荷}}=\ef\frac{q}{r}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
d.
 电势的叠加 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V_{\text{点电荷系}}=\sum_{i}V_{i}=\sum_{i}\ef\frac{q_{i}}{r_{i}}=\int_{Q}\dd V=\int_{Q}\ef\frac{\dd q}{r}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
二.
 导体和电介质
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 导体的静电平衡条件
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
最终形态: 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{\text{内}}=0,E_{\text{外表面}}=\frac{\sigma}{\eqs_{0}}.$
\end_inset

导体是等势体, 其内无净电荷导体存在时静电场的分布
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
2.
 电介质
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
(a) 场强分布: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec E=\vec{E_{0}}/\eqs_{r}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(b) 电偶极矩: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec p=q\vec l$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
(c) 极化强度: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec P=n\vec p$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec D$
\end_inset

的Gauss定理
\begin_inset Formula $\oint_{S}\vec E\cdot\dd\vec S=\frac{1}{\eqs_{0}}\sum\left(q_{0\text{内}}+q_{\text{内}}^{'}\right),$
\end_inset

意味着
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\oint_{S}\vec D\cdot\dd\vec S=\sum q_{0\text{内}},D=\eqs_{0}\eqs_{e}\vec E.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
应用: 
\uwave on
\color teal
用Gauss定理求对称性电场分布: 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
球体: 
\begin_inset Formula $D4\pi r^{2}=q_{in}\implies E=\frac{q_{in}}{\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}4\pi r^{2}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
圆柱体: 
\begin_inset Formula $D2\pi rh=q_{in}\implies E=\frac{q_{in}}{\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}2\pi rh}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
平面: 
\begin_inset Formula $D2S_{\text{底}}=q_{in}\implies E=\frac{q_{in}}{\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}2S_{\text{底}}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
4.
 电容 
\begin_inset Formula $C=Q/U$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
三类电容器的电容
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
5.
 电场能量: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
W_{e}=\frac{QU}{2}=\frac{CU^{2}}{2}=\frac{Q^{2}}{2C}=\red{\int_{\Omega}\frac{1}{2}DE\dd V}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
三.
 磁场
\begin_inset FormulaMacro
\newcommand{\mf}[1]{\frac{\mu_{0}I}{#1}}
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 磁场的Biot-Savart定律: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vec B=\int_{I}\dd\vec B=\int_{I}\mf{4\pi}\frac{\dd l\times\vec{e_{r}}}{r^{2}}.
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
2.
 磁场的叠加: 
\begin_inset Formula $B=\sum_{i}\vec{B_{i}.}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
模型磁场: 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
直线 
\begin_inset Formula $B=\mf{4\pi r}(\cos\theta_{2}-\cos\theta_{1})$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
圆弧 
\begin_inset Formula $B=\mf{2r}\frac{\phi}{2\pi}$
\end_inset

, 方向与电流方向成右手螺旋的关系.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 磁场的Gauss定理和环路定理
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
Gauss定理 
\begin_inset Formula $\oint_{S}\vec B\cdot\dd\vec S=0.$
\end_inset

(无源)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
环路定理 
\begin_inset Formula $\oint_{L}\vec B\cdot\dd\vec l=\mu_{0}\sum I_{\text{内}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
应用: 用环路定理求对称性磁场的分布
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
无限长直线.
 
\begin_inset Formula $B=\mf{2\pi r}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
螺线管.
 
\begin_inset Formula $B=n\mu_{o}I$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
螺线环.
 
\begin_inset Formula $B=\frac{N\mu_{0}I}{2\pi r}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
四.
 磁力
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 Lorentz力 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{F_{m}}=q\vec v\times\vec B$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
a.
 螺旋运动, 
\begin_inset Formula $R=\frac{mv_{\perp}}{qB},h=\frac{2\pi mv_{//}}{qB}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
2.
 Ampere力 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec F=\int_{L}\dd\vec F=\int_{L}I\dd\vec l\times\vec B,\dd\vec F=nS\dd lq\vec v\times\vec B=I\dd\vec l\times\vec B$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
3.
 磁矩: 
\begin_inset Formula $p_{m}=IS\vec{e_{n}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
4.
 磁力矩: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec M=\vec{p_{m}}\times\vec B$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
五.
 电磁感应
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
1.
 电磁感应定律: 
\begin_inset Formula $\eqs=-\frac{\dd\phi_{m}}{\dd t},\phi_{m}=\int_{S}\vec B\cdot\dd\vec S$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
2.
 动生电动势: 
\begin_inset Formula $\eqs=\int_{L}(\vec v\times\vec B)\cdot\dd\vec l$
\end_inset

, 其中非静电力是
\begin_inset Formula $\vec f=\vec v\times\vec B.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
3.
 感生电动势: 
\begin_inset Formula $\eqs=-\frac{\dd\phi_{m}}{\dd t}=\int_{S}\frac{\partial\vec B}{\partial t}\dd\vec S$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
特例.
 非静电力
\begin_inset Formula $E_{i}$
\end_inset

圆柱形均匀磁场的变化激发
\begin_inset Formula $E_{i}2\pi r=\frac{\dd B}{\dd t}S$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
