begin{circuitikz} 
\backslash
tikzstyle{every node}=[font=
\backslash
LARGE] 
\backslash
draw [, line width=0.5pt ] (2.25,11.75) rectangle (5.5,7.5); 
\backslash
draw [line width=0.5pt](4,11.75) to[L ] (4,10.25); 
\backslash
draw [, line width=0.5pt ] (3.75,10.25) rectangle (4.25,9.75); 
\backslash
draw [ line width=0.5pt, -Stealth] (6,10) -- (6,11.5); 
\backslash
node [font=
\backslash
LARGE] at (6.5,10.5) {}; 
\backslash
draw [ line width=0.5pt, -Stealth] (6,10) -- (6,11.5); 
\backslash
draw [ line width=0.5pt, -Stealth] (6,10) -- (6,11.5); 
\backslash
end{circuitikz}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $a\sqrt{m/k}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 设
\series bold
弹簧的伸长量为
\series default

\begin_inset Formula $x_{0}$
\end_inset

, 选择向上为正方向, 于是起始时刻受力分析: 
\begin_inset Formula $F_{\text{弹}}-mg=ma$
\end_inset

, 意味着
\begin_inset Formula $k\Delta x-mg=ma\implies\Delta x=\frac{m(a+g)}{k}.$
\end_inset

根据机械能守恒, 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{1}{2}k(\Delta x)^{2}=\frac{1}{2}mv^{2}+mg\Delta x$
\end_inset

.
 因此
\begin_inset Formula $v_{max}=\sqrt{\frac{m}{k}}a.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(2-9)光滑的水平桌面上放置一固定的圆环带, 半径为
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

, 一 物体贴着环带的内侧运动, 如图所示, 物体与环带间的滑动 摩擦系数为
\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

, 设物体在某一时刻经A点时的速率为 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{0}$
\end_inset

, 求 此后
\begin_inset Formula $t$
\end_inset

 时间物体的速率以及从
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

点开始所经过的路程.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
begin{circuitikz} 
\backslash
tikzstyle{every node}=[font=
\backslash
LARGE] 
\backslash
draw (5.5,8) circle (2.75cm); 
\backslash
draw (5.5,8) circle (2.75cm); 
\backslash
draw (5.5,8) circle (2.5cm); 
\backslash
draw (7.25,10) rectangle (7.5,9.75); 
\backslash
draw [ -Stealth] (5.5,8) -- (8,8); 
\backslash
draw [ -Stealth] (5.5,8) -- (8,8); 
\backslash
end{circuitikz}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $s=\frac{R}{\mu_{k}}\ln\frac{R+v_{0}\mu_{k}t}{R}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 对于任意的一个时刻, 沿着切向分析, 有
\begin_inset Formula $F_{t}=f=\mu F_{N},$
\end_inset

沿着法向分析, 有
\begin_inset Formula $F_{n}=\frac{mv^{2}}{R}.$
\end_inset

z直到
\begin_inset Formula $a_{t}=\frac{\mu v^{2}}{R}.$
\end_inset

展开, 有
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\dd v}{\dd t}=\frac{mv^{2}}{R},$
\end_inset

得到方程式
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\dd v}{v^{2}}=\frac{v^{2}}{R}\dd t$
\end_inset

, 两边同时对初始状态和末了状态积分, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\int_{v_{0}}^{v_{\text{末}}}\frac{\dd v}{v^{2}}=\int_{0}^{t}\frac{v^{2}}{R}\dd t
\]

\end_inset

解得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
v_{\text{末}}=\frac{1}{\frac{\mu}{R}t+\frac{1}{v_{0}}}.
\]

\end_inset

然后把
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

展开为
\begin_inset Formula $\dd s/\dd t$
\end_inset

, 对两边同时做定积分就可以求出路程
\begin_inset Formula $s=\frac{R}{\mu_{k}}\ln\frac{R+v_{0}\mu_{k}t}{R}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(2-15)一个初速度
\begin_inset Formula $v_{0}$
\end_inset

从地面上竖直向上抛出质量为
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

的小球, 小球除了受重力外, 还受到一个大小为
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha mv^{2}$
\end_inset

的粘滞阻力(
\begin_inset Formula $\alpha$
\end_inset

是常数, 
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

是小球的运动速率).
 求小球回到地面的时候的速率.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $v_{1}=\frac{v_{0}\sqrt{g}}{\sqrt{\alpha v_{0}^{2}+g}}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 如果一心想着一下子求出来, 就会陷入困境.
 我们把这个问题转化为求上升和下降两段路程的问题, 最后让他们相等即可.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
以向上为正方向, 上升过程中, 有
\begin_inset Formula $-ma_{1}=-mg-f.$
\end_inset

因为
\begin_inset Formula $a=\frac{\dd v}{\dd x}\frac{\dd x}{\dd t}=v\frac{\dd v}{\dd x},$
\end_inset

原式变为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{v}{g+\alpha v^{2}}\dd v=\dd x
\]

\end_inset

两边同时积分, 有
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{v_{0}}^{0}\frac{v}{g+\alpha v^{2}}\dd v=\int_{0}^{h}\dd x$
\end_inset

, 解得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
h_{1}=-\frac{1}{2a}\left(\ln\frac{g}{g+\alpha v_{0}^{2}}\right).
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
另外一方面, 考虑下来的时候, 进行受力分析, 
\begin_inset Formula $-mg+f=-ma_{2}.$
\end_inset

 同理, 有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
h_{2}=-\frac{1}{2a}\left(\ln\frac{g-\alpha v_{m}}{g}\right).
\]

\end_inset

因为
\begin_inset Formula $h_{1}=h_{2},$
\end_inset

解答得
\begin_inset Formula $v_{m}=\frac{v_{0}\sqrt{g}}{\sqrt{\alpha v_{0}^{2}+g}}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(3-13)有一运送砂子的皮带以恒定的速率
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

水平运动, 砂子经一静止 的漏斗垂直落到皮带上, 忽略机件各部位的摩擦及皮带另一端的其 它影响, 试问：(1) 若每秒有质量为
\begin_inset Formula $M'=\dd M/\dd t$
\end_inset

的砂子落到皮带上,  要维持皮带以恒定速率
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

运动, 需要多大的功率? (2)若
\begin_inset Formula $M'=100$
\end_inset

kg/s, 
\begin_inset Formula $v=0.5$
\end_inset

m/s, 水平牵引力多大? 所需功率多大? 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $P=v^{2}M',50$
\end_inset

N,
\begin_inset Formula $25$
\end_inset

W.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 对于任意时刻分析, 设有
\begin_inset Formula $\dd m$
\end_inset

这样大的沙子落入传送并且获得速度, 那么
\begin_inset Formula $\dd I=\dd m\cdot v.$
\end_inset

根据
\begin_inset Formula $F=\frac{\dd I}{\dd t}=v\frac{\dd m}{\dd t},$
\end_inset

那么
\begin_inset Formula $P=Fv=v^{2}\frac{\dd m}{\dd t}.$
\end_inset

第二问带入数据即可.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(4-14) 质量
\begin_inset Formula $m$
\end_inset

的匀质链条, 置于桌面, 链条与桌面的摩擦系数为
\begin_inset Formula $\mu$
\end_inset

,  下垂端的长度为
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

, 在重力作用下, 由静止开始下落, 求链条完全 滑离桌面时重力、摩擦力的功.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


