\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

图, 对物体进行受力分析, 
\begin_inset Formula $Mg-T=ma_{t}$
\end_inset

.
 对于滑轮分析, 
\begin_inset Formula $TR=J\beta.$
\end_inset

但是对于右图, 
\begin_inset Formula $MgR=J\beta.$
\end_inset


