\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega=3v_{0}/4L,\theta=\cos^{-1}\left(1-\frac{v_{0}^{2}}{4gL}\right).$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 对于(1), 可以使用角动量守恒
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
mvL=\left(mL^{2}+\frac{1}{3}mL^{2}\right)\omega
\]

\end_inset

就可以求得.
 对于(2), 考虑机械能守恒, 就有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{1}{2}\left(\frac{1}{3}mR^{2}+mR^{2}\right)\omega^{2}=\left(\frac{1}{2}mgL(1-\cos\theta)\right)+mgL(1-\cos\theta).
\]

\end_inset

注意刚体是要看重心移动的距离.
 
\end_layout

