\begin_layout Example
(课上例题) 现在有如下所示的问题.
 原先, 球
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

带有电荷
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

, 球
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

带有电荷
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

.
 现在将球
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

接地, 这时候求球各个表面的电势分布.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
incfig{probgex}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $V_{A}=\frac{q'}{4\pi\eqs_{0}R_{0}}+\frac{-q'}{4\pi\eqs_{0}R_{1}}+\frac{Q+q'}{4\pi\eqs_{0}R_{2}}=0,q'=\frac{R_{0}R_{1}Q}{R_{0}R_{2}-R_{1}R_{2}-R_{0}R_{1}}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 我们发现
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的电势是0.
 那么考虑
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的电荷分布变为了
\begin_inset Formula $q'.$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $Q_{B\text{内表面}}=-q',Q_{B\text{外表面}}=Q+q'.$
\end_inset

 那么列出
\begin_inset Formula $V_{A}=0$
\end_inset

的式子:
\begin_inset Formula $V_{A}=\frac{q'}{4\pi\eqs_{0}R_{0}}+\frac{-q'}{4\pi\eqs_{0}R_{1}}+\frac{Q+q'}{4\pi\eqs_{0}R_{2}}=0$
\end_inset

; 解之即可.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(8(1)-10) 两块大导体平板, 面积
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, 带电量分别为
\begin_inset Formula $Q_{1}$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $Q_{2}$
\end_inset

, 证明相对 两个面总是带等量异号电荷, 相背两个面总是带等量同号电荷,  并求各面电荷密度.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
incfig{prob810}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{1}=\sigma_{4}=(Q_{1}+Q_{2})/2S;Q_{2}=-Q_{3}=(Q_{1}-Q_{2})/2S.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 取贯穿两个内部的面作为Gauss面, 因为通过Gauss面的电力线条数为0.
 但是电荷包围的电荷是可以计算的.
 因此我们就可以写作
\begin_inset Formula $\oint\vec E\cdot\dd\vec s=0=\frac{Q_{\text{内}}}{\eqs_{0}}=\frac{\sigma_{1}+\sigma_{2}}{\eqs_{0}}S_{\text{底}}$
\end_inset

, 也就是
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{2}+\sigma_{3}=0.$
\end_inset

 接着, 我们考虑场强叠加加上静电平衡条件
\begin_inset Formula $E_{\text{内}}=0,$
\end_inset

在介质内任取一点, 得到
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{1}-\sigma_{2}-\sigma_{3}-\sigma_{4}=0.$
\end_inset

 最后, 根据电荷守恒, 就得到了
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{1}+\sigma_{2}=Q_{1}/S;\sigma_{3}+\sigma_{4}=Q_{2}/S.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(8(1)-11) 三块大导体平板, 面积
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

, 中间一块带电
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

 ,  其余条件见图.
 (1)当
\begin_inset Formula $ab$
\end_inset

断开的时候求各面电荷密度.
 (2)用导线连接
\begin_inset Formula $ab$
\end_inset

, 求各面的电荷密度.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
incfigw{prob811}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: (1) 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{1,3,4,6}=Q/2S;Q_{2,5}=-Q/2S$
\end_inset

; (2) 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{1.6}=Q/2S;\sigma_{2}=-\sigma_{3}=2Q/3S;\sigma_{4}=-\sigma_{5}=Q/3S.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 对于(1)而言, 考虑选择两个类似的Gauss面, 分别贯穿
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

的下表面, 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

的上表面; 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

的下表面, 
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

的上表面, 这样就与上一题有类似的
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sigma_{2}+\sigma_{3} & =0\qquad(1);.\\
\sigma_{4}+\sigma_{5} & =0\qquad(2)
\end{align*}

\end_inset

 接下来运用
\begin_inset Formula $C$
\end_inset

板的内容里面的场强之和为0的信息, 就有
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma_{1}+\sigma_{2}+\sigma_{3}+\sigma_{4}+\sigma_{5}-\sigma_{6}=0\qquad(3)
\]

\end_inset

.
 最后用电荷守恒的式子, 就有
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
\sigma_{3}+\sigma_{4} & =0\qquad(4);\\
\sigma_{1}+\sigma_{2} & =0\qquad(5);\\
\sigma_{5}+\sigma_{6} & =0\qquad(6).
\end{align*}

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
对于(2)而言, 由于
\begin_inset Formula $A,C$
\end_inset

之间连了线, 电荷可以自由跑动, 于是
\begin_inset Formula $(5),(6)$
\end_inset

应当改写为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\sigma_{1}+\sigma_{2}+\sigma_{5}+\sigma_{6}=0\qquad(7).
\]

\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $A,C$
\end_inset

两板因为相连而等势, 选取
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\frac{\sigma_{3}}{\eqs_{0}}d=\frac{\sigma_{4}}{\eqs_{0}}2d\qquad(8)
\]

\end_inset

.
 联立求解即可.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
对于式子
\begin_inset Formula $(3),$
\end_inset

如果改写成在
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

板子, 
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

板子里面列方程, 是等效的, 这样是重复的条件(也就是线性相关的), 对我们的方程组解答没有大影响.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(8(2)-6) 平行板电容器中一半空间充满介质, 极板带电
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

时, 求极板 间电场和电势差.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
incfig{prob86}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $U=E_{2}d=\frac{2Qd}{\eqs_{0}S(\eqs_{r}+1)}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 考虑因为两板之间的电势差是恒定的, 因此在介质的分界面上电荷会重新分布.
 考虑左侧的面密度为
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{1},$
\end_inset

右侧的为
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{2}.$
\end_inset

 下面选取合适的Gauss面求场强.
 
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align*}
D_{1} & =\sigma_{1};\\
D_{2} & =\sigma_{2};\\
E_{1} & =\frac{\sigma_{1}}{\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}};\\
E_{2} & =\frac{\sigma_{2}}{\eqs_{0}}.
\end{align*}

\end_inset

 电势差相等, 
\begin_inset Formula $E_{1}d=E_{2}d$
\end_inset

, 并且
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma_{1}+\sigma_{2}=2Q/S.$
\end_inset

 由此可以得到
\begin_inset Formula $E_{2}=\frac{2Q}{\eqs_{0}S(\eqs_{r}+1)}$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
电容器
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
1.
 电容
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
定义: 
\begin_inset Formula $C\equiv Q/U.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
通常求法: 假设带电
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

, 求电场, 积分求电势
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

, 使用定义求之.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
击穿电压: 最大是沿最大场强的积分.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
2.
 若干个特殊物体的电容: 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
孤立导体球的电容: 
\begin_inset Formula $C=4\pi\eqs_{0}R$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
平行板电容器的电容: 
\begin_inset Formula $C=\frac{\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}S}{d}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
柱形电容器的电容: 
\begin_inset Formula $C=2\pi\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}L\left(\ln\frac{R_{2}}{R_{1}}\right)^{-1}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 电容器的串并联
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
并联: 
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

相等, 
\begin_inset Formula $C=\frac{Q_{1}+Q_{2}+\cdots+Q_{n}}{U}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
串联: 
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

相等, 
\begin_inset Formula $C=\frac{1}{C_{1}}+\frac{1}{C_{2}}+\frac{1}{C_{3}}+\cdots+\frac{1}{C_{n}}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
判别方法: 同一根导线连接, 
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

相等, 若干个极板连着极板, 
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

相等.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
4.
 电容器的储能: 
\begin_inset Formula $W=\int\dd W=\int_{0}^{Q}U\dd q=\int_{0}^{Q}\frac{q}{C}\dd q=\frac{Q^{2}}{2C}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
另外的公式: 带入
\begin_inset Formula $Q=CU$
\end_inset

做恒等变换, 得
\begin_inset Formula $W=\frac{CU^{2}}{2}=\frac{QU}{2}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Example
(8(2)-5) 平行板电容器中插入一介质板, 求电容.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
incfig{prob85}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $C=\frac{3\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}S}{(2\eqs_{r}+1)d}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 假设带电, 并且面密度
\begin_inset Formula $D=\frac{Q}{S}=\sigma,E_{0}=\frac{\sigma}{\eqs_{0}},E_{1}=\frac{\sigma}{\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}}.$
\end_inset


\begin_inset Formula $U=E_{0}\frac{2d}{3}+E_{1}\frac{d}{3}.$
\end_inset

于是就可以根据
\begin_inset Formula $C=\frac{Q}{U}$
\end_inset

得到答案.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(8(2)-9) 这里有一个液位计, 内部导体圆柱半径为
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

, 外面导体圆筒的半径为
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

, 高 为
\begin_inset Formula $H$
\end_inset

.
 液体的相对介电常数为
\begin_inset Formula $\eqs_{r}$
\end_inset

,  求电容与液位高度
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

的关系.
 
