\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
C=\frac{\lambda_{2}(H+(\eqs_{r}-1)x)}{\frac{\lambda}{2\pi\eqs_{0}}\ln\frac{R}{r}}
\]

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 设电荷线密度介质部分,真空部分分别为
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1},\ensuremath{\lambda_{2}.}$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $D_{1}=\frac{\lambda_{1}}{2\pi r},D_{2}=\frac{\lambda_{2}}{2\pi r}$
\end_inset

.
 求出
\begin_inset Formula $E,$
\end_inset

然后因为
\uwave on
\color purple
电势差相等
\uwave default
\color inherit
, 就有
\begin_inset Formula $\int_{r}^{R}E_{1}\dd r=\int_{r}^{R}E_{2}\dd r$
\end_inset

, 并且电荷守恒有
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda_{1}+\lambda_{2}(H-x)=Q$
\end_inset

, 就可以解答.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(8(2)-12)平行板电容器面积为
