\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

相同, 因此可以用
\begin_inset Formula $Q^{2}/2C;$
\end_inset

并联
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

相同, 因此可以用
\begin_inset Formula $CU^{2}/2.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(8(2)-11) 两个电容均为C的电容器带电量分别为
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

和
\begin_inset Formula $2Q$
\end_inset

, 求并联后 极板电量和能量增量.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 电量增量: 都为
\begin_inset Formula $\left(3/2\right)Q;$
\end_inset

能量增量为
\begin_inset Formula $-Q^{2}/4C$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 先求总电量
\begin_inset Formula $q_{1}+q_{2}=3Q.$
\end_inset

由于电压相同进行重新分配, 也就是
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{q_{1}'}{C_{1}}=\frac{q_{2}'}{C_{2}}\implies q_{1}'=q_{2}'.$
\end_inset

根据
\begin_inset Formula $W=\frac{Q^{2}}{2U}$
\end_inset

就可以得到值.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
电场的能量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
1.
 电场的能量公式: 
\begin_inset Formula $W=\int_{(a)}^{(b)}DE\dd V.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(综合复习题) 半径为
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

的导体球和内、外分别为
\begin_inset Formula $2R$
\end_inset

、
\begin_inset Formula $3R$
\end_inset

的导体球壳同心放 置, 其间有均匀电介质, 相对介电常数为
\begin_inset Formula $\eqs_{r}$
\end_inset

.
 若给外导体球壳带电 
\begin_inset Formula $Q$
\end_inset

, 并将内球接地, 求：(1)各表面的带电量；(2)电场分布；(3)导体 球和球壳的电势差；(4)电场的总能量
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 这个答案太复杂了, 问问老师到时候算出答案能不能不带入.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: (1) 设内球带电量为
\begin_inset Formula $q,$
\end_inset

那么从内到外的各个电荷量为
\begin_inset Formula $q,-q,Q+q.$
\end_inset

 (2) 先求
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

的大小, 再求
\begin_inset Formula $E$
\end_inset

的大小.
 从内到外的各个
\begin_inset Formula $D$
\end_inset

分别是
\begin_inset Formula $E_{1}=0,E_{2}=\frac{q}{4\pi r^{2}},E_{3}=0,E_{4}=\frac{Q+q}{4\pi r^{2}};$
\end_inset

各个电场分别是
\begin_inset Formula $E_{1}=0,E_{2}=\frac{q}{4\pi\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}r^{2}},E_{3}=0,E_{4}=\frac{Q+q}{4\pi\eqs_{0}r^{2}}.$
\end_inset

(3)电势差积分即可.
 (4) 表达式为
\begin_inset Formula $W=\int_{0}^{\infty}\frac{1}{2}DE\green{\dd V}=\int_{R}^{2R}\frac{1}{2}D_{2}E_{2}\green{4\pi r^{2}\dd r}+\int_{3R}^{\infty}\frac{1}{2}D_{4}E_{4}\green{4\pi r^{2}\dd r}=\frac{4\pi q^{2}}{16\pi^{2}r^{4}\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}}\cdot\frac{7R}{3}-\frac{4\pi(Q+q)^{2}}{16\pi^{2}r^{4}\eqs_{0}}\cdot\frac{27R}{3}.$
\end_inset

但是我们现在还不知道
\begin_inset Formula $q$
\end_inset

, 根据
\begin_inset Formula $U$
\end_inset

导体球电势为0, 可以得到方程式
\begin_inset Formula $U=\frac{q}{4\pi\eqs_{0}\eqs_{r}}\left(\frac{1}{R}-\frac{1}{2R}\right)+\frac{Q+q}{4\pi\eqs_{0}}\frac{1}{3R}=0.$
\end_inset

于是知道
\begin_inset Formula $q=\frac{-Q\eqs_{r}}{\eqs_{r}-3}.$
\end_inset

 带入原方程就行了.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Section
磁场中的常见问题
\end_layout

\begin_layout Subsection*
恒定电流与其激发的磁场
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
1.
 电流
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
形成: 载流子的定向移动形成电流
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
传导电流.
 载流子在电场作用下的定向移动
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
运流电流.
 带电体的机械运动
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
位移电流.
 与电场的变化有关
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
强度.
 单位时间内通过任一截面的电量.
 
\begin_inset Formula $I=\lim_{\Delta t\to0}\frac{\Delta q}{\Delta t}=\frac{\dd q}{\dd t}=neSu$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $n$
\end_inset

是数密度; 
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

是横截面面积; 
\begin_inset Formula $u$
\end_inset

是电子的漂移速率.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
线,面上的电流状况
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
体电流的面密度.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\sigma=\frac{\dd I}{\dd S_{\perp}}$
\end_inset

(A/m
\begin_inset Formula $^{2}$
\end_inset

)
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
面电流的线密度.
 
\begin_inset Formula $j=\frac{\dd I}{dl_{\perp}}$
\end_inset

(A/m)
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
2.
 电源和电动势
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
a.
 电路 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
内电路: 外力克服静电场力做功, 将电荷从低电位转移到高电位
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
外电路: 电荷在电场的作用下由高电位到低电位形成电流.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
b.
 电动势: 把单位正电荷从电源负极移动到正极, 非静电力做的功.
 
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
方向: 外电路从高到低, 内电路从低到高.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
3.
 特殊运动情形下的电流
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
a.
 圆电流: 带电体绕定点的旋转
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
均匀带电杆子.
 圆面电流
\begin_inset Formula $\dd I=\frac{\lambda\dd r}{\frac{2\pi}{\omega}}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
均匀带电圆盘.
 圆面电流
\begin_inset Formula $\dd I=\frac{\sigma2\pi r\dd r}{\frac{2r}{\omega}}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
4.
 磁场
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
a.
 特性: 运动电荷周围存在磁场, 
\series bold
磁场对周围运动电荷有力的作用
\series default
; 是物质, 客观存在;
\series bold
服从叠加原理
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
b.
 磁感应强度
\begin_inset Formula $\vec B$
\end_inset

.
 速度为
\begin_inset Formula $v$
\end_inset

的运动电荷
\begin_inset Formula $q_{0}$
\end_inset

受Lorentz力
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
大小: 
\begin_inset Formula $f_{m}=q_{0}vB\sin\theta$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
方向: 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{f_{m_{\text{max}}}}\times\vec v.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
单位: T
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
c.
 磁感应线.
 描述磁场空间分布的假想的曲线
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
关系.
 切线方向为
\begin_inset Formula $\vec B$
\end_inset

的方向, 数密度为
\begin_inset Formula $\vec B$
\end_inset

的大小: 
\begin_inset Formula $B=\frac{\dd\varphi_{m}}{dS_{\perp}}$
\end_inset

, 又称为磁通密度.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
性质.
 (1) 无头无尾的闭合曲线; (2) 曲线方向与电流成右手螺旋; (3) 曲线与电流相互铰链.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
d.
 曲面
\begin_inset Formula $S$
\end_inset

的磁通量.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\varphi_{m}=\int_{S}\vec B\cdot\dd\vec S$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
e.
 磁场的Gauss定理: 
\begin_inset Formula $\oint_{S}\vec B\cdot\dd\vec S=0.$
\end_inset

 这表明了磁场没有原, 但是有旋.
 
\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Description
5.
 常见内容的磁场极其叠加
\begin_inset FormulaMacro
\newcommand{\dl}{I\dd\vec l}
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Description
a.
 电流元
\begin_inset Formula $I\dd\vec l$
\end_inset

的磁场.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\dd\vec B=\frac{\mu}{4\pi}\frac{\dl\times\vec{e_{r}}}{\green{r^{2}}},$
\end_inset

其中, 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{e_{r}}$
\end_inset

的方向是当前的微元指向要判定的点的矢量.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
b.
 载流直导线的磁场.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec B=\frac{\mu_{0}I}{4\pi a}\left(\cos\theta_{1}-\cos\theta_{2}\right)\vec e$
\end_inset

.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Description
c.
 圆环中心轴线距离
\begin_inset Formula $x$
\end_inset

处上的磁场: 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\mu_{0}I}{2}\frac{R}{x^{2}+R^{2}}\frac{R}{\sqrt{x^{2}+R^{2}}}$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\end_deeper
\begin_layout Example
(9(1)-6) 有一闭合回路由半径为 
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

 和 
\begin_inset Formula $b$
\end_inset

 的两个同心共面半圆连接而成,  如图其上均匀分布线密度为 
\begin_inset Formula $\lambda$
\end_inset

 的电荷, 当回路以匀角速度 
\begin_inset Formula $\omega$
\end_inset

 绕 过 
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

 点垂直于回路的轴转动时, 求圆心 
\begin_inset Formula $O$
\end_inset

 点处的磁感应强度.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\mu_{0}\lambda\omega}{2\pi}\left(\pi+\ln\frac{b}{a}\right)$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 分为两个部分: 圆面电流和直线电流.
 首先来看圆面电流: 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{a}=\frac{q}{T}=\frac{\lambda\pi a}{2\pi/\omega}=\frac{1}{2}\lambda a\omega.$
\end_inset

 
\begin_inset Formula $B_{0}=\frac{\mu_{0}I_{a}}{2a}.$
\end_inset

同理可以看到另一个小圆环的情形.
 他们的方向竖直向外.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
接下来看直线段的电流: 其上电荷元
\begin_inset Formula $\dd q$
\end_inset

旋转形成等效的圆电流.
 也就是
\begin_inset Formula $\dd I_{r}=2\frac{\dd q}{T}=2\frac{\lambda\dd r}{2\pi/\omega}=\frac{\omega}{\pi}\lambda\dd r.$
\end_inset

这个方向向外.
 然后我们求这一小段的
\begin_inset Formula $\dd\vec B$
\end_inset

的大小.
 
\begin_inset Formula $\dd B_{r}=\frac{\mu_{0}\dd I}{2\pi r}$
\end_inset

.
 积分之后就可以得到.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(课堂练习17-2) 在一半径为
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

的无限长半圆柱形 金属薄片中, 自上而下地有电流强度
\begin_inset Formula $I$
\end_inset

 通过, 如图示, 试求圆柱轴线任一点
\begin_inset Formula $P$
\end_inset

 处的磁感应强度.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
incfig{ring}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 沿
\begin_inset Formula $y$
\end_inset

轴负向, 大小为
\begin_inset Formula $-\frac{\mu_{0}I}{\pi^{2}R}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 由于这是和圆面有关的, 于是使用极(柱)坐标系考虑.
 于是
\begin_inset Formula $\dd I=\frac{I\dd r}{\pi R}=\frac{IR\dd\theta}{\pi R}.$
\end_inset

 那么电流元的磁感应强度大小为
\begin_inset Formula $\dd B=\frac{\mu_{0}\dd I}{2\pi r}.$
\end_inset

 从
\begin_inset Formula $0\to2\pi$
\end_inset

积分即可.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Separator plain
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
(课堂练习17-4) 在半径为
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

及
\begin_inset Formula $r$
\end_inset

 的两圆周之间, 有总匝数为
\begin_inset Formula $N$
\end_inset

的均匀密绕 平面螺线圈如图示, 当导线中通有电流I时,求螺线圈中心点（即两圆圆心）处的磁感应强度 .
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
incfig{ex174}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
答案: 
\begin_inset Formula $\frac{\mu_{0}NI}{2(R-r)}\ln\frac{R}{r}.$
\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Example
分析: 取半径为
\begin_inset Formula $a$
\end_inset

, 宽度为
\begin_inset Formula $\dd a$
\end_inset

的窄环, 则电流为
\begin_inset Formula $\dd I=\frac{N}{R-r}I\dd a.$
\end_inset

那么
\begin_inset Formula $\dd B_{\text{圆心}}=\frac{\mu_{0}\dd I}{2\pi a}.$
\end_inset

积分即可.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
