\begin_inset Formula $B2\pi r=\mu_{0}NI.$
\end_inset

同样根据定义
\begin_inset Formula $\phi_{m}=N\varphi_{m}=N\int_{S}B\dd S=N\int_{R_{1}}^{R_{2}}\frac{N\mu_{0}I}{2\pi r}h\dd r$
\end_inset

.
 
